161.2	Chuck_Palahniuk	Chuck Palahniuk	Charles Michael "Chuck" Palahniuk (born February 21, 1962) is an American transgressional fiction novelist and freelance journalist. He is best known for the award-winning novel Fight Club, which was later made into a feature film. He lives near Portland, Oregon and spends time in Washington near Seattle.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/e4/Palahniukmic.jpg/250px-Palahniukmic.jpg
